// PF2e Magic Items (banded)
// =====================================================================
// Real PF2e items (Foundry pf2e system data), banded by settlement
// size on TWO axes: level cap AND rarity. Small settlements stock
// common items only; towns add uncommon; cities add rare. Non-common
// items are tagged, e.g. "Frost Brand *(uncommon)*". ORC/OGL content
// reused with attribution — see ATTRIBUTION.
//
// Entry: [@PF2eMagic with <size>]  where <size> is a Town Forge tier:
//   hamlet | village | small_town | town | large_town | small_city |
//   city | large_city | metropolis  (thorpe = hamlet alias)
// A bare [@PF2eMagicAny] rolls from the full list (all levels/rarities).

Title: PF2e Magic Items (banded)

